## Async Await

<!-- livebook:{"reevaluate_automatically":true} -->

```elixir
defmodule Async do
  def invoke(func, args \\ []) do
    GenServer.call(EventLoop, {:invoke, func, args})
  end

  def await(pid) do
    GenServer.call(EventLoop, {:await, pid})
  end
end
```

## Application

<!-- livebook:{"reevaluate_automatically":true} -->

```elixir
IO.inspect(self())

outer =
  Async.invoke(fn ->
    IO.inspect(self())

    inner =
      Async.invoke(fn ->
        IO.inspect(self())

        42
      end)

    v = Async.await(inner)

    2 * v
  end)

IO.puts(Async.await(outer))
